Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [9/5/2023]

This privacy policy governs the use of the Muslim Life Guide app and outlines how the App collects, uses, and discloses personal information. By using the App, you agree to the terms of this policy.

Information Collection and Use

The Muslim Life Guide app is dedicated to enhancing your spiritual experience and does so by providing access to religious resources and prayer time information. To offer you the best experience, the App may use the following types of information:

Location Services: In order to provide you with accurate prayer times and Qibla direction based on your current location, the App may request access to your device's location data. This data is used solely for the purpose of determining prayer times and Qibla direction and is not stored or shared with third parties.

We do not collect or store any other personal information from its users. The App only provides access to the Quran, Adkaar, and prayer time information. We do not collect any additional user data, including device information or usage data.

Third-Party Services

The Muslim Life Guide app does not use any third-party services that collect personal information from users. We are committed to ensuring your data remains secure and confidential.

Security

The Muslim Life Guide app takes robust measures to protect the personal information of its users. We use secure servers to store any information we collect. Your location information, which is solely used for providing prayer times, is processed securely on your device and is not transmitted to our servers.

Changes to this Policy

The Muslim Life Guide app may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices and to comply with legal requirements. We will notify users of any material changes by updating the date at the top of this policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, or if you wish to inquire about the data we collect or request its deletion, please contact us at mahdiababneh37@gmail.com.

Thank you for using the Muslim Life Guide app to enrich your spiritual journey.
